♪ WALK ACROSS THE ROOM
AND OPEN UP THE WINDOW ♪

37:36.885 --> 37:39.588
IT'S FOR YOU.

37:39.588 --> 37:40.889
♪ AND THE SUNLIGHT ♪

37:40.889 --> 37:43.432
YOU MADE IT
JUST UNDER THE WIRE.

37:43.432 --> 37:44.993
WELL, I GUESS
IT'S MY LUCKY NIGHT.

37:44.993 --> 37:47.536
NO.

37:47.536 --> 37:49.598
SOMEHOW I THINK IT'S MINE.

37:49.598 --> 37:52.541
♪ LIFE IS FINE,
I FEEL SO YOUNG ♪

37:52.541 --> 37:57.446
♪ THE WORLD IS WONDERFUL ♪

37:57.446 --> 37:58.677
(slurps)

37:58.677 --> 38:00.709
HE MAKES IT SO EASY
FOR ME TO HATE HIM.

38:00.709 --> 38:02.581
HOW DID YOU STAY WITH HIM
ALL THESE YEARS?

38:02.581 --> 38:05.454
THAT'S A COMPLICATED QUESTION,
DANIEL.

38:05.454 --> 38:07.456
AND I DON'T WANT TO TURN YOU
AGAINST YOUR FATHER.

38:07.456 --> 38:09.688
OH, DON'T WORRY.
HE'S DOING IT ALL BY HIMSELF.

38:09.688 --> 38:13.362
I'VE HIRED A LAWYER,
DANIEL.

38:13.362 --> 38:14.723
IT MIGHT GET UGLY.

38:14.723 --> 38:17.466
AND I DON'T WANT TO COST YOU
YOUR POSITION IN THE COMPANY.

38:17.466 --> 38:19.628
DON'T WORRY.
I'M STAYING WITH THE COMPANY.

38:19.628 --> 38:20.769
I'LL HAVE ACCESS
TO DAD'S BUSINESS ACCOUNTS,

38:20.769 --> 38:21.930
BANK RECORDS.

38:21.930 --> 38:23.432
WHATEVER YOU NEED,
I'LL GET IT.

38:23.432 --> 38:24.703
AS FAR AS I'M CONCERNED,

38:24.703 --> 38:26.575
WHATEVER YOU WANT
IN THIS DIVORCE IS YOURS.

38:26.575 --> 38:27.806
(inhales)

38:27.806 --> 38:29.638
(exhales deeply)

38:29.638 --> 38:31.039
I THINK I'M GONNA
STAY HERE TONIGHT,

38:31.039 --> 38:32.811
KEEP AN EYE ON THINGS.

38:32.811 --> 38:35.313
THANK YOU.

38:41.390 --> 38:42.621
(Nolan)
YOU CROSSED THE LINE, EMILY.

38:42.621 --> 38:43.952
HOW COULD YOU DO THAT TO ME?

38:43.952 --> 38:45.854
IF YOU MEAN THAT RECORDING
OF YOU AND TYLER,

38:45.854 --> 38:47.696
YOU'LL THANK ME ONE DAY.
I DID YOU A FAVOR.

38:47.696 --> 38:49.027
BUT I TRUSTED YOU.

38:49.027 --> 38:51.630
YOU CAN'T BUILD TRUST
ON SECRETS, NOLAN.

38:51.630 --> 38:52.761
YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT
BY NOW.

38:52.761 --> 38:54.032
OH, YOU'RE ONE TO TALK--

38:54.032 --> 38:56.034
HOLDING BACK ON ME ABOUT AMANDA,
GOD KNOWS WHAT ELSE.

38:56.034 --> 38:59.368
YOU HAVE BEEN TRYING TO
DERAIL ME SINCE DAY ONE--

38:59.368 --> 39:01.370
TOYING WITH JACK'S HEART,

39:01.370 --> 39:03.942
BUYING HIS BOAT.

39:03.942 --> 39:05.874
AND NOW YOU SABOTAGED
OUR ALLIANCE

39:05.874 --> 39:07.716
BECAUSE YOU FELL
FOR A HOOKER.

39:07.716 --> 39:11.079
(chuckles)

39:11.079 --> 39:12.781
THE DIFFERENCE IS,

39:12.781 --> 39:17.025
THAT WHEN I HAD AN OPPORTUNITY
TO EXPOSE YOU TODAY,

39:17.025 --> 39:18.727
I DIDN'T.

39:18.727 --> 39:20.389
WELL, MAYBE THAT'S BECAUSE,
DEEP DOWN INSIDE,

39:20.389 --> 39:21.690
YOU KNOW I MEANT IT
WHEN I SAID

39:21.690 --> 39:24.663
THAT I WOULD TAKE YOU DOWN
IF YOU TRIED TO GET IN MY WAY.

39:27.636 --> 39:29.798
MESSAGE RECEIVED.

39:31.099 --> 39:34.102
I'M DONE PLAYING
YOUR EVIL GAMES.

39:35.373 --> 39:37.045
(door opens)

39:37.045 --> 39:39.778
I NEVER ASKED YOU
TO BE A PART OF THIS.

39:40.979 --> 39:43.782
NO.

39:43.782 --> 39:47.085
YOUR FATHER DID.

39:47.085 --> 39:49.688
EMS, HE DIDN'T WANT THIS
FOR YOU.

39:49.688 --> 39:51.760
REMEMBER?

39:51.760 --> 39:54.423
IT'S GOOD THAT HE'S GONE.

39:55.864 --> 39:57.766
'CAUSE AT LEAST NOW
HE CAN'T SEE

39:57.766 --> 39:59.728
WHAT YOU'VE BECOME.

40:04.903 --> 40:08.036
(cell phone rings)

40:08.036 --> 40:10.809
(ring)

40:10.809 --> 40:12.781
(ring)

40:12.781 --> 40:14.783
(exhales)

40:14.783 --> 40:16.785
(ring)

40:16.785 --> 40:18.186
(rings and beeps)

40:18.186 --> 40:19.648
HI.

40:19.648 --> 40:22.120
HEY, UH, DID I JUST SEE
NOLAN LEAVING YOUR PLACE?

40:22.120 --> 40:23.822
YEAH, UM...

40:23.822 --> 40:25.123
HE HAD

40:25.123 --> 40:26.825
a pretty scary visit
from Tyler.

40:26.825 --> 40:28.797
He thinks Nolan
got him fired.

40:28.797 --> 40:31.560
WELL, THAT'S JUST IT.
MY FATHER DIDN'T FIRE HIM.

40:31.560 --> 40:34.162
REALLY?

40:34.162 --> 40:36.465
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA WHY?

40:36.465 --> 40:37.806
WHO KNOWS?

40:37.806 --> 40:39.468
I'VE JUST HAD ENOUGH
OF MY FATHER'S LIES.

40:39.468 --> 40:40.809
(sighs)

40:40.809 --> 40:42.971
LISTEN, ARE YOU OKAY WITH ME
STAYING WITH MY MOM TONIGHT?

40:42.971 --> 40:45.043
IF AND WHEN TYLER SHOWS UP,

40:45.043 --> 40:46.515
I don't want her here alone.

40:46.515 --> 40:49.047
(sighs) YEAH, THAT'S
PROBABLY A GREAT IDEA.

40:49.047 --> 40:50.879
I MEAN, YOU'RE WELCOME TO
COME OVER, TOO, IF YOU LIKE.

40:50.879 --> 40:52.881
GOT A GREAT VIEW
OF YOUR PORCH FROM UP HERE

40:52.881 --> 40:55.654
IN CASE AMANDA CLARKE
COMES DIGGING AROUND AGAIN.

40:55.654 --> 40:56.955
I can handle Amanda.

40:56.955 --> 40:58.857
You just look after your mom.

40:58.857 --> 41:00.228
AH, SHE'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

41:00.228 --> 41:02.060
SHE HIRED A LAWYER TODAY.

41:02.060 --> 41:04.593
THAT'S GREAT.

41:06.735 --> 41:08.667
SLEEP TIGHT.

41:08.667 --> 41:10.769
Night.

41:10.769 --> 41:13.902
(beeps)

41:13.902 --> 41:15.844
DID I HEAR YOU SAY
AMANDA CLARKE?

41:15.844 --> 41:18.046
YEAH, SHE'S BACK IN TOWN
AFTER ALL THIS TIME.

41:18.046 --> 41:19.978
STRANGE, RIGHT?

41:21.880 --> 41:23.852
(Emily) MY FATHER WROTE,

41:23.852 --> 41:26.855
"ALWAYS QUESTION
WHERE YOUR LOYALTIES LIE.

41:26.855 --> 41:29.718
"THE PEOPLE YOU TRUST
WILL EXPECT IT,

41:29.718 --> 41:32.691
"YOUR GREATEST ENEMIES
WILL DESIRE IT,

41:32.691 --> 41:33.862
"AND THOSE
YOU TREASURE THE MOST,

41:33.862 --> 41:36.825
WILL, WITHOUT FAIL,
ABUSE IT."

41:36.825 --> 41:38.697
(man's voice)
"DEAR MR. CLARKE,

41:38.697 --> 41:39.868
"I AM WRITING TO INFORM YOU

41:39.868 --> 41:41.730
"THAT I WILL NOT
BE MOVING FORWARD

41:41.730 --> 41:43.872
"WITH THE APPEAL
OF YOUR CONVICTION

41:43.872 --> 41:46.074
FOR THE CRIME OF TREASON."

41:46.074 --> 41:47.776
(door opens)

41:47.776 --> 41:48.937
(keys jangle)

41:48.937 --> 41:51.640
(blows air)

41:51.640 --> 41:52.681
(drops objects on desk)

41:52.681 --> 41:53.782
(keys jangle)

41:53.782 --> 41:54.783
RYAN HUNTLEY.

41:56.715 --> 41:57.886
WHO ARE YOU?

41:57.886 --> 41:58.987
AMANDA CLARKE.

41:58.987 --> 42:01.890
HOW DID YOU GET IN HERE?

42:01.890 --> 42:04.092
THAT'S THE LEAST
OF YOUR PROBLEMS RIGHT NOW.

42:06.955 --> 42:10.028
I WANT TO KNOW WHY
YOU DROPPED MY FATHER'S APPEAL.

42:12.300 --> 42:16.835
(Emily) SOME SAY LOYALTY
INSPIRES BOUNDLESS HOPE.

42:16.835 --> 42:18.567
AND WHILE THAT MAY BE,

42:18.567 --> 42:20.809
THERE IS A CATCH.

42:20.809 --> 42:25.143
TRUE LOYALTY
TAKES YEARS TO BUILD...

42:25.143 --> 42:27.946
AND ONLY SECONDS TO DESTROY.
